document_data.name: Merchants' Pack
document_data.mainbody: '''Merchants' pack''' was a seafood dish served at [[Tulmene's Tower]] inn, located in the town of [[Tulmene]] in [[Tethyr]].
document_data.Description: Tulmene's Tower was one of the busiest and one of the more expensive establishments in town. It was known for the so-called merchants' pack. The dish was [[fish]] baked in a hand loaf of [[bread]], stuffed with [[onion]]s, [[mushroom]]s, and [[spice]]s.
